select pogMarketingFeedBaseTab as pogId
        ,sum(saleNmpu*pogWeightage)/sum(pogWeightage) as NMSO
        ,sum(saleNmpu*pogWeightage*(1-cancellationPer))/sum(pogWeightage) as NMBO
        ,sum((saleNmpu-totalFixedFfcMarketingFeedBaseTab+laapFixedFfcMarketingFeedBaseTab)*pogWeightage)/sum(pogWeightage) as NM3SO
        ,sum((saleNmpu-totalFixedFfcMarketingFeedBaseTab+laapFixedFfcMarketingFeedBaseTab)*pogWeightage*(1-cancellationPer))/sum(pogWeightage) as NM3BO
from(
    select distinct *
    from marketingFeedBaseTable
    ) a
group by pogMarketingFeedBaseTab
","temp.pogs_salenmso")

run(sql="
    select date, count(distinct subOrderId) as orders, count(distinct case when lower(Channel) like 'fb%' then subOrderId end) as FB_Orders, count(distinct case when lower(utmContent) like '%cpt%' then subOrderId end) as CPT_Orders  
    from (
            select c.date, c.pogId, c.subOrderId, d.Channel, d.utmContent 
            from(
                select to_date(FROM_UNIXTIME((b.orderDate)/1000)) as date, a.pogId, b.subOrderId 
                from `temp.p` a left join `all(agCmDump)` b 
                on a.pogId=b.pogId 
                where DATEDIFF(current_date(),to_date(FROM_UNIXTIME((b.orderDate)/1000))) between 1 and 5
                ) c
            left join `temp.attributed_Orders` d
            on c.subOrderId=d.subOrderId
        ) group by date order by date
",1000)
